<anchor id="flashfs_8h_1flashfs"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Wrapper class for file system access. The class uses the littlefs implementation provided by Zephyr File System library. See <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/apidoc/latest/group__flash__area__api.html">for Flash Area Interface details</ulink> and <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/latest/services/file_system/index.html">for File System API details</ulink>..</para>
</simplesect>
